INSERT INTO `case_studies` VALUES (9,1048,'2010-12-21','Long Law Offices',NULL,NULL,'<p>+Develop branding that does not subscribe to traditional corporate styles and colors<br />\r\n+Create a website that is friendly and easy to use</p>','<p>AG Design took the traditional concept of using initials as a logo, and gave it an unconventional twist. By linking the letters together and using vibrant colors, the logo appears welcoming. An equally friendly and vibrant website is developed to compliment the logo.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>',NULL,'study__20101222111831.jpg','study__20101222121853.jpg',NULL,NULL,'pdf20110210113053.pdf','Branding with an Unconventional Flare',NULL,NULL,1,'2011-05-18 19:25:14','2010-12-21 17:23:22'),(11,1048,'2010-12-22','Triage Consulting',NULL,NULL,'<p>+ Out-dated website look &amp; feel<br />\r\n+ Focused too heavily on recruitment<br />\r\n+ Updating content took too long</p>','<p>The navigation and layout of the site is re-organized, giving it a more modern look. The re-organization makes information more accessible, providing a user-friendly feel. The site can still facilitate recruitment without heavily empahsizing this. A customized Content Management System (CMS) means updating photos, profiles and content can be done simply and easily.</p>',NULL,'study__20101222170518.jpg','study__20101222170532.jpg',NULL,NULL,'pdf20110210112803.pdf','\"Arlene and her firm did an amazing job of re-designing our company\'s website. I was consistently impressed by the quality and value of her work, and by the amazing client service she provided over and over again. Our clients and employees give the new site rave reviews - it exactly captures the brand message we hoped to communicate.\"','Shawn Tienken','Principal',1,'2011-06-02 10:42:42','2010-12-22 09:44:19'),(16,1048,'2010-12-22','Inspired In-Law',NULL,NULL,'<p>+ Develop a brand that is both meaningful and creative <br />\r\n+ Develop a brand that resonates with their target audience: the elderly and children of the elderly</p>','<p>AG Design developed a logo that artfully integrates their commitment to sustainability and family-living. The unique logo is unlike those of similar products, easily resonates with several demographics. <br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>',NULL,NULL,'study2__20101222123333.jpg','study3__20101222123333.jpg',NULL,'pdf20110210112927.pdf','\"Arlene has been a consummate professional in all of our design tasks never missing a deadline or a detail. Working with Arlene and her talented staff has exceeded our expectations! I highly recommend her firm.\"','Joshua Larson','Principal',1,'2011-06-02 10:43:16','2010-12-22 12:33:33'),(19,1048,'2010-06-12','Cal Document Preparers',NULL,NULL,'<p>+ Changing names from &quot;For The People&quot; to &quot;California Document Preparers&quot; (CDP)<br />\r\n+CDP needed to be re-branded within 4 weeks and still remain functional<br />\r\n+ The rebrand needed to be complete with collateral and a new website</p>','<p>AGD worked quickly to develop a brand that was similar in look and feel to their previous brand, so as to make the change as easy on their current clientele as possible. Once the brand was solidified, all printed material and advertisements had to be changed and updated. AGD even undertook a PR campaign to inform people of their name change.&nbsp;</p>',NULL,'study__20110621134814.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,'pdf20110621114740.pdf','\"The team at AG Design is awesome! They did a spectacular job designing my business\'s logo, materials, and website. The AG Staff are full of ideas for helping manage your marketing, and they are very good at follow-through. We have been working with them for long enough to be able to see good results from their efforts.\"','Ian Duncan','Co-Owner',1,'2011-06-21 13:00:24','2011-02-10 16:59:08'),(18,1048,'2011-01-15','Executive Mindshare',NULL,NULL,'<p>+ Develop UI (User Interface) &amp; UX (User Experience) that appeals      to industry professionals<br />\r\n+ Create presentations and collateral geared towards increasing sponsors      and investors<br />\r\n+ Program iPad and mobile phone apps that support the Executive      Mindshare Platform</p>','<p>The goal was to develop a User Experience that was modern, approachable and innovative.                 AGD made industry news, updates and premium content the focal point of the User Experience.              Other unique features include: a customized video newscast, access to industry-related podcasts, syncing of other social media and discussion panels. AGD also developed collateral and a demo video aimed at attracting investors.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',NULL,NULL,'study__20110628124608.jpg',NULL,NULL,'pdf20110628160635.pdf','\"I can\'t say enough good things about the team at AG Design. Not only do they provide amazing, professional work, but they go above and beyond to help our business succeed. They have come through on critical last minute projects and hit unthinkable deadlines, all while creating innovative and inspiring design. [They] are the kind of professionals every organization wishes they had 10 of!!\r\nWe are so glad to be working with [them]!\"','Tania Hyatt','Director of Operations',1,'2011-10-27 15:04:35','2011-02-10 14:04:09'),(20,1048,'2010-10-14','ILR',NULL,NULL,'<p>+ Develop a logo and brand that resonated on a professional and personal level<br />\r\n+ Develop a website that is accessible to all of ILR&rsquo;s client base; this includes those with visual and hearing impairment <br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>','<p>AGD created a logo that is both symbolic and professional. A website was developed with incorporated assistive technology, so that those with visual or hearing impairments can interact with the site.&nbsp;</p>',NULL,'study__20110621135836.jpg',NULL,'study__20110621135851.jpg',NULL,'pdf20110621120635.pdf','\"AGD has that perfect mix of creativity and business savvy, and when assisting us with design and implementation of a rebranding effort, gave us fantastic ideas and a solid plan.\"','Paula McElwee','Executive Director',1,'2011-06-21 12:58:54','2011-02-10 17:14:08'),(21,1048,'2011-10-26','Shop Bubble Belly',NULL,NULL,'<p>+ Transfer existing shopping cart to an improved ecommerce shopping cart<br />\r\n+ Incorporate merchant payment services<br />\r\n+Increase purchase completion rate <br />\r\n+ Develop a custom, client operated, Shopping Cart Manger</p>','<p>AGD streamlined the shopping experience so that Bubble Belly can accept major credit cards on the website, rather than route them elsewhere. AGD&nbsp;also developed  a custom, back-end Shopping Cart Manager, allowing Bubble Belly to update and track inventory, monitor sales, track orders, and program sales and discount offers. As an added bonus, AGD created a member Wishlist, allowing members to create a list of desired items (great for baby shower registries and expectant mothers).</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',NULL,'study__20111027153600.jpg',NULL,'study__20111027153544.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'2011-10-27 15:13:42','2011-10-27 14:26:56'),(22,1048,'2011-08-18','UC Berkeley ',NULL,NULL,'<p>+ Develop a website with a      unique design that is consistent with the UC brand<br />\r\n+ Construct a Content Management System (CMS) that would give the client      optimal control &amp; flexibility<br />\r\n+ Develop a simple,      client managed Search Engine Optimization (SEO) management solution</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','<p>AGD incorporated images of UC      Berkeley&rsquo;s distinct Greek architecture. This gave the site a fresh      appearance while remaining true to the established University of      California brand. AGD then developed a sophisticated,      custom, back-end CMS tool, that allows the Rhetoric Department to easily manipulate      content, images, and navigation menus, while maintaining the integrity of      the design. An integrated CMS      tool empowers UCB administrators to add SEO meta-tags, descriptions,      tiles and keywords on every page.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',NULL,'study__20111027163100.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,'2011-10-27 15:31:08','2011-10-27 15:17:58');
