g, Trade Show Displays.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>About the City:</div>\r\n<div>Belmont is a city in San Mateo County, California, United States. It is in the San Francisco Bay Area, located half-way down the San Francisco Peninsula between San Mateo and San Carlos. It was originally part of the Rancho de las Pulgas, for which one of its main roads, the Alameda de las Pulgas, is named. The town was incorporated in 1926. Ralston Hall, built around a villa formerly owned by Count Cipriani, an Italian aristocrat, by Bank of California founder William Chapman Ralston, on the campus of Notre Dame de Namur University is a historic landmark. The locally famous &quot;Waterdog Lake&quot; is located in the foothills and highlands of Belmont.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>The City of Belmont is located at</div>\r\n<div>One Twin Pines Lane</div>\r\n<div>Belmont, CA 94002</div>\r\n<div><a href=\\\"http://www.belmont.gov/\\\">http://www.belmont.gov/</a></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Belmont Chamber of Commerce is located at</div>\r\n<div>1059A Alameda De Las Pulgas</div>\r\n<div>Belmont, CA 94002</div>\r\n<div><a href=\\\"http://www.belmontchamber.org/\\\"><span>www.<b>belmontchamber</b>.org</span></a></div>\r\n</p>',NULL,2,2,NULL,1,1,'AGD is a full service Creative Agency and Marketing Firm, serving all bay area cities including Belmont, CA. We can also work with clients all over the country and world. AG Design Group also provides iPhone and Android mobile application development.','Web Design Belmont CA, Marketing Belmont CA, Graphic Design Belmont CA, Web Design Belmont ','Belmont Web Services','belmont','3,9','2011-10-20 17:01:54','2011-10-20 00:00:00'),(1116,12,NULL,NULL,9,NULL,NULL,NULL,'delete this page','delete this page','delete this page','\r\n\r\n','Author Here','Upfront Value',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p>delete this page</p>\r\n<div class=\"note_body commentable_icon_position_reference\" style=\"margin-right: 30px; z-index: 2; position: relative; font-family: \'lucida grande\', verdana, sans-serif; text-align: left; \"><span class=\"hover_target\" hover_container=\"show_note_6331916\" style=\"z-index: 2; \"><highlightable hover_container=\"show_note_6331916\" style=\"z-index: 2; \"> </highlightable></span></div>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'delete-this-page','3,9','2011-11-09 10:31:08','2011-11-09 00:00:00'),(1117,1040,2,NULL,5,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Startup Package',NULL,'Startup Package',NULL,'\"The AGD Startup Package gave us the competitive advantage and professional look needed for our investor pitches.  This provided us the unbelievable value upfront for our company as we have to manage costs through the funding rounds.\"','Author Here','Startup Venture',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'<div style=\"padding-top: 5px; padding-right: 5px; padding-bottom: 5px; padding-left: 5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; \">\r\n<div>\r\n<h3>\r\n<div style=\"font-size: 12px; \">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</h3>\r\n<div><strong>AGD STARTUP PACKAGE<br />\r\n</strong>&bull; Logo &amp; ID System&#8232;<br />\r\n&bull; UI/UX Design for Prototype<br />\r\n&nbsp; (6-8 slides that most-likely get worked into the actual design)&#8232;<br />\r\n&bull; Media Kit<br />\r\n&bull; Business Plan<br />\r\n&bull; Investor PPT &amp; Slide Deck&#8232;<br />\r\n&bull; Presentation Training&#8232;<br />\r\n&bull; Press Release<br />\r\n&bull; 5-8 Page Website (to host the above collateral and investor pitch video)</div>\r\n<div>&bull; SEO Service</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><strong>VALUE&nbsp;</strong></div>\r\n<div>$25,000 worth of Design / Marketing / Strategy / Communication work</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><strong>TERMS</strong></div>\r\n<div>&#8232;Deposit: $7,500</div>\r\n<div>&#8232;Repayment: $500/mo until balance is paid&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<hr />\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><b>About the AGD Startup Package</b></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>The AGD Startup Package is offered by AG Design Group Inc., for pre-screened and qualified startup companies that are starting to get into the Angel funding pipeline. The AGD Startup Package utilizes the services of <strong>AG Design</strong> and <strong>AGD interactive</strong> (AGD-i), the two parts that make up AG Design Group, Inc.&nbsp; The package is offered to companies primarily seeking&nbsp;Series Seed or Series A funding.&nbsp; It provides a strong alternative to companies with limited <span id=\"lblContent\">early-stage capital</span> in assisting them through their investment rounds.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>We\'ve had a lot of startup sucess, helping early-stage companies enhance and enrich their value proposition, giving them a strong competitive advantge in the <span id=\"lblContent\">investment community</span><span id=\"lblContent\"> of accredited private equity investors, venture capitalists and corporate/institutional investors. </span></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<hr />\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><strong>About AGD interactive</strong></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>AGD interactive<b>&nbsp;</b>(AGD-i) is a high growth, next generation interactive marketing firm specializing in creating meaningful customer engagement in online environments. AGD-i is a part of AG Design Group, Inc., a full service Creative Agency and Marketing Firm.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<p>AGD-i offers customers a variety of ways to keep their audience informed and engaged. From traditional web applications and social media integration to custom mobile applications, the creative team at AGD-i continues to integrate current and emerging technologies to deliver cost efficient solutions for our clients. Complementing its Interactive marketing expertise, AGD-i is a leader in emerging technologies, content management platforms, web publishing platforms, and social media platforms; helping customers achieve feature-rich functionality with rapid, cost-effective development.</p>\r\n<p>AGD-i specializes in interactive, digital marketing, mobile and social media application development and provides a robust suite of solutions for companies to develop and support highly relevant social media applications and integrated digital marketing campaigns.</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p><strong>About AG Design</strong></p>\r\n<div>Founded in 2006, AG Design is part of AG Design Group, Inc., a full  service Creative Agency and Marketing Firm. AG Design Group, Inc. is a   Women-Owned and Minority-Owned Small Business headquartered in Walnut   Creek, California. We are located steps from San Francisco and Silicon   Valley in the heart of Northern California&rsquo;s Bay Area. We have proven   capabilities in executing coast-to-coast projects for clients from San   Francisco to New York, and have partnered with teams in Europe and Asia.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Our  Team strives to achieve professional design, direction, and   communication success for our clients. Our success and the success of   our clients, take the form of company growth, identification, brand   recognition, design innovation, and return on investment. We specialize   in tailoring our services to our client&rsquo;s needs &ndash; combining innovative   approaches with unparalleled resources, make AG Design Group a premier   choice in the Creative Marketing industry.</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal; \">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<hr style=\"font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal; \" />\r\n<div style=\"font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal; \">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><strong>FAQs</strong></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><strong>Q: Can anyone receive this package?</strong></div>\r\n<div>A: No. You must be prescreened and qualify.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><strong>Q: What are the requirements to qualify?&#8232;</strong></div>\r\n<div>A: We look to see if the concept of your product or service is viable. &nbsp;You should have a business plan and monetization model, a rough cut is okay. &nbsp;We also look at the founders\' financial picture, either through background checks, credit checks, bank statements, tax returns, or other means. &nbsp;You should also have a counselor/advisor, we recommend <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.eastbayscore.org/\">SCORE</a> counselors to ensure you have proper guidance and are navigating the investment routes.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><a href=\"http://agdesigngroup.net/contact-us\">Contact us</a> to schedule a meeting and give us your elevator pitch.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><strong>Q: Why does AGD offer this package?&#8232;</strong></div>\r\n<div>A: We know there are a lot of great ideas out there and people have inadequate ways of showing them. People have a million dollar idea, and we give them the competitive advantage by helping them look like a million bucks, so they can get funding for a million (or whatever investment amount they are targeting). By offering this package, startup companies can get a jump-start on their business and be well equipted to impress potential investors by looking professional and having all the tools for the &quot;WOW&quot; effect. &nbsp;It&rsquo;s one thing to tell an investor about an idea, and another to show them; and we&rsquo;ll make sure they are blown away by the designs.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><strong>Q: Why does AGD require the $7,500 deposit?</strong></div>\r\n<div>&#8232;A: All investors want to see that the founder spent some of their own money on their concept, we do as well. We want to make sure the company we invest our time in is serious and has &lsquo;skin in the game&rsquo; and a vested interest to push the company forward.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><strong>Q: Why is there a $500/mo fee?</strong></div>\r\n<div>&#8232;A: This is your repayment to us for our upfront investment into your company. We are investing well over 150 hours into your company upfront and are taking on risk. The $500/mo payment is a way we, as an investor, mitigate that risk and ensues we don&rsquo;t have total loss. This also creates the motivation to push forward in seeking funding, rather than sitting idle.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div><strong>Q: Are the terms negotiable?&nbsp;</strong></div>\r\n<div>&#8232;A: We evaluate every company independently of one another. &nbsp;This is something we address on a case-by-case basis.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div><strong>Q: What are the terms for the work you provide?&nbsp;</strong></div>\r\n<div>&#8232;A: We provide our standard terms sheet prior to executing a contract and agreement.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><strong>Q: Why do you invest all this time upfront and take on this risk?&#8232;</strong></div>\r\n<div>A: We invest this time upfront and do everything we can to get your business funded. We have a vested interest in your company, and when you get funded, we get paid out in full. Chances are, that when you get funded, you&rsquo;ll use us to complete the UI/UX and develop your full online product or application. As you grow, we grow with you and have the full scalability to support all of your marketing needs as well.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><strong>Q: Why don&rsquo;t you invest money instead of time?&#8232;</strong></div>\r\n<div>A: We&rsquo;ve worked with a lot of startups and know what it takes to get funded. If an investor can visualize what your product will look like, you&rsquo;re a step ahead. This is the best way we can ensure our investment is spent on delivering high quality material, taking the guessing away from the investors. Several of our clients have been funded and our designs were carried through to the final production.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><strong>Q: Do you have examples of Start-up Companies you\'ve worked with?</strong></div>\r\n<div>&#8232;A: Yes. See below.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<table width=\"500\" cellspacing=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" border=\"1\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Biomindshare</td>\r\n            <td>$1.5MM Seed Funded, seeking $4MM Series A&#8232;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Swarmology</td>\r\n            <td>$750k Seed Funded&#8232;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Asthma Signals</td>\r\n            <td>Undisclosed Self Funded, Seeking Seed Funding</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>SquareTracker</td>\r\n            <td>$80k Self Funded, Seeking Seed Funding</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&#8232;Rival Zone</td>\r\n            <td>Undisclosed Seed Funded&#8232;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Intela Labs</td>\r\n            <td>Undisclosed Self Funded&#8232;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Faithworks&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td>Seeking Seed Funding</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&#8232;Page 1 Properties</td>\r\n            <td>$700k Seed Funded, Seeking $1.5MM Series A</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&#8232;Inspired In-Law&nbsp;</td>\r\n            <td>Self Funded</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.agdesigngroup.net/contact-us\">Contact us</a> for samples of the work we\'ve done for these companies.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,'New Company Startup Package','New Company Startup, Venture, Investor','AG Design Startup Package','agd-startup-package','3,9','2011-11-22 16:37:19','2011-11-09 00:00:00');
