INSERT INTO `people` VALUES (4,1043,'01','Arlene',NULL,'Santos','President & Creative Director','925.954.7084','arlene@agdesigngroup.net',NULL,'<p>Arlene brings over a decade of creative design and strategic marketing experience. Arlene has lead teams that have designed and executed hundreds of marketing campaigns and design projects, collecting award-winning results along the way.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAfter receiving Bachelor of Fine Arts (BFA) degrees in Graphic Design from the University of San Francisco (USF) and California College of the Arts and graduating Magna-Cum-Laude, Arlene began freelancing, building her clientele since 2001. By attending the top design school for Graphic Design, Arlene was mentored by leaders and innovators of the Graphic Design industry.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nArlene is well received by her clients and bases her success on the success of each client and the results they achieve. She has created long lasting relationships with clients that lead to ongoing projects and campaigns. She contributes her success to her design process, strong work ethic, and dedication to projects.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nArlene actively participates in her community and servers in the local Chamber of Commerce as well as sits on the board of directors for Mt. Diablo Business Women.</p>',NULL,'<p>My iPhone</p>','<p>Slow Drivers</p>','<p>Bora Bora &amp; Moorea<br />\r\n(French Polynesia)</p>','<p>Mommy and Baby Books. Maybe the latest FB posts...</p>','<p>Mommy and Baby Books. Maybe the latest FB posts...</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,'photo__20110519181007.jpg','on','2011-10-13 11:49:51','2010-12-17 13:44:36'),(5,1043,'05','Perlita',NULL,'H.','Communications Manager','925 954 7084','perlita@agdesigngroup.net',NULL,'<p>Perlita adds a flare to the AG Design team. Poised, articulate and with a penchant for dry humor, Perlita keeps the joy de vivre at AGD. She graduated from the University of California in Berkeley, with a B.A. in Mass Communications. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nWith a vast and eclectic background, from interning at KTVU News to conducting wine seminars and tastings, Perlita&rsquo;s rich life experiences gives her a unique approach to marketing. When she is not fiddling with words, Perlita enjoys dabbling in the culinary arts and preparing sensuous meals paired with delectable wines.</p>',NULL,'<p>Baby Wipes</p>','<p>Mondays, Traffic and Gasoline Prices</p>','<p>The O.co<br />\r\nRAAAAAIDERRRRRRRS!</p>','<p>My Email</p>','<p>My Email</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,'photo__20110519180912.jpg','on','2011-11-15 15:31:17','2010-12-20 18:16:26'),(7,1043,'10','Jennifer',NULL,'V.','Senior Designer','925 954 7084','jenn@agdesigngroup.net',NULL,'<p>Jennifer brings over ten years of experience to AG Design. After graduating at the top of her class from American University in Washington D.C., Jennifer honed her craft on the East Coast designing and developing brands for a wide variety of corporate and non-profit organizations, including the Smithsonian, Howard University and the National Cathedral.</p>\r\n<p class=\\\"txtMain\\\">Originally from California, Jennifer is delighted to be back on the West Coast. When she isn&rsquo;t pairing beautiful typography with vivid imagery, Jennifer explores the Bay Area in search of good eats, antique and thrift store treasures, and scenic running trails.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',NULL,'<p>Cheese</p>','<p>Laziness</p>','<p>Saint Lucia</p>','<p>Realtor Flyers</p>','<p>Realtor Flyers</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,'photo__20110519181100.jpg','on','2011-11-15 15:28:55','2010-12-27 16:33:50'),(8,1043,'20','Sara',NULL,'S.','Lead Programmer','925 954 7084','sara@skyhighsoftware.com',NULL,'<p>Sara has over 25 years of experience in software development.&nbsp; She has a unique ability to create innovative technical solutions to business challenges.&nbsp; Translating these years of experience into top-notch skills for web development, Sara helps AG Design create websites that are not only visually appealing but also technically advanced, including features such as custom content management, members-only areas and custom e-commerce shopping carts, databases, PO&nbsp;Systems and more. <br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\nSara believes the key to her success is in leveraging her technical skills to support a client&rsquo;s business vision and productivity.</p>',NULL,'<p>A PC&nbsp;and the Internet</p>','<p>Waiting in Line</p>','<p>VIVA Las Vegas!</p>','<p>The Woman Behind the New Deal by Kirsten Downey</p>','<p>The Woman Behind the New Deal by Kirsten Downey</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,'photo__20110519181125.jpg','on','2011-11-15 15:32:46','2010-12-27 16:36:45'),(10,1043,'99','Morgan',NULL,'G.','Executive Assistant',NULL,'morgan@agdesigngroup.net',NULL,'<p>Morgan keeps the AGD office and team operating in prime condition. Her extensive office managment skills were developed through years of managing large office buildings. Her savvy and ability to multi-task make her an invaluable member to the team.</p>\r\n<p>When she is not hard at work in the AGD office, Morgan is attending Contra Costa Community College to get her EMT license.</p>',NULL,'<p>My Cell Phone</p>','<p>Lazy People</p>','<p>Cabo San Lucas&nbsp;</p>','<p>Shawn Hannity</p>','<p>Shawn Hannity</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,'photo__20110404154302.jpg',NULL,'2011-11-15 15:33:15','2011-01-19 22:50:00'),(12,1043,'15','Thuy ',NULL,'P.','Junior Designer ',NULL,'Thuy@agdesigngroup.net',NULL,'<!--StartFragment-->\r\n<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\">Thuy is an East Bay Area native, hailing from Concord. Her interest in design began at an early age, and she attended California State University of the East Bay majoring in Multimedia. Thuy has developed her craft working for the likes ZipZoomfly (an online retailer) and the City of Concord where she used her design skills to develop several marketing campaigns and strategies.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(38, 38, 38);\\\">The experience Thuy has gained from working in both corporate and government arenas, give her the ability to work well with differing design strategies and styles. Thuy&rsquo;s combination of designer and HTML skills make her an incredible asset to the AGD Team. In her spare time, Thuy enjoys yoga, cooking and shopping.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<!--EndFragment-->\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<!--EndFragment-->',NULL,'<p>Chocolate</p>','<p>Messy Spaces</p>','<p>Hawaii</p>','<p>Nothing at the moment. Although the Twilight Series is one of my favorites.</p>','<p>Nothing at the moment. Although the Twilight Series is one of my favorites.</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,'photo__20110404154158.jpg','on','2011-11-15 15:33:57','2011-02-17 14:19:39'),(13,1043,'90','Shawn',NULL,'M.','Multimedia Coordinator',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<!--StartFragment-->\r\n<p style=\\\"\\\" class=\\\"MsoNormal\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: Helvetica; color: black;\\\">Shawn is AGD&rsquo;s in-house musician and multimedia guru. A graduate of California State University in the East Bay, Shawn received top honors in Business Marketing. His extensive communications background as a Public Speaking Coach and Social Media Consultant at Provident Credit Union, have contributed to his innovative approach to multimedia. His specialties include video production and editing, as well as developing interactive social media hubs.</span></p>\r\n<p>When he is out of the office you can find Shawn on stage singing and playing the guitar. He considers his music to be an alternative fusion of acoustic reggae pop.</p>\r\n<!--EndFragment-->\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>',NULL,'<p>My Ukulele</p>','<p>Instant Mashed Potatoes</p>','<p>Puerto Vallarta</p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'photo__20110404154222.jpg',NULL,'2011-07-28 17:00:06','2011-02-21 11:30:05');
