INSERT INTO `portfolio` VALUES (1,1053,'UCB','UCB','1',NULL,'<p>AGD developed a new look for the UC Berkeley Rhetoric Department website. The classic design style is paired with easy navigation and optimal functionality through a custom Content Management System (CMS).&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>+Web Design<br />\r\n+Custom CMS</p>','portfolio__20110503164005.jpg',NULL,NULL,'2010-12-21'),(2,1053,'EXM','Executive Mindshare','1',NULL,'<div>. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Executive Mindshare is an exemplary example of AGD&rsquo;s skill for developing User Interface (UI) and User Experience (UX). AGD melds modern design with a progressive and highly interactive user experience for this business-oriented social network.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>UI &amp; UX&nbsp; /&nbsp; Corporate Collateral&nbsp;&nbsp; /&nbsp; Investor Presentation&nbsp; /&nbsp; Media Kit&nbsp; /&nbsp; eNewsletter Design&nbsp; /&nbsp; Mobile Application&nbsp; /&nbsp; Multimedia Video</div>','portfolio__20110527170104.jpg','on',NULL,'2010-12-21'),(3,1053,'TCG','Triage Consulting','1',NULL,'<p>. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .</p>\r\n<p>A comprehensive and multi-faceted website is developed for this multi-billion dollar company. The website includes a custom designed Content Management System (CMS) which allows the user to update and change their site easily.</p>\r\n<p>Web Design&nbsp; /&nbsp; Custom CMS&nbsp; /&nbsp; Internal Presentations and Collateral</p>','portfolio__20110527171320.jpg','on',NULL,'2010-12-21'),(4,1053,'CDP','CA Document Preparers','1',NULL,'<p>. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .</p>\r\n<p>California Document Preparers underwent a complete re-brand after they broke away from their franchise. The new logo needed to retain the same look and feel, but be different enough to distinguish themselves as a separate entity. The re-brand was matched with a comprehensive marketing strategy which included printed advertisements, mailers and online presence.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Logo Rebrand&nbsp; /&nbsp; Business Collateral&nbsp; /&nbsp; Brochure &amp; Marketing Pieces&nbsp; /&nbsp; Print Advertising&nbsp; /&nbsp; Social Media /&nbsp; Trade Show Graphics&nbsp; /&nbsp; Website with CMS</p>','portfolio__20110527161611.jpg','on',NULL,'2010-12-21'),(26,1053,'TPS','Gourmet Pour','1',NULL,'<div>. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .    . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .  .   . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Gourmet Pour looked to AGDesign for a modern and memorable logo. AGD&nbsp;delivered a logo that cleanly illustrated purpose. The logo was carried forward to expressive and graphic packaging design.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Branding&nbsp; /&nbsp; Packaging</div>','portfolio__20110527150352.jpg','on',NULL,'2011-05-27'),(27,1053,'SFI','SF Dental Imaging','1',NULL,'<p>. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .  . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .  . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>SF&nbsp;Dental Imaging came to AGD with the request for an updated, sophisticated logo with clean lines and simple elegance.</p>','portfolio__20110527152352.jpg','on',NULL,'2011-05-27'),(5,1053,'LSA','Inspired In-Law','1',NULL,'<div>. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>This new product, a subsidiary brand of Larson and Shores Architects, underwent an extensive identity study and branding. AGD further developed their brand through print advertisements, marketing collateral and a website.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Branding&nbsp; /&nbsp; Stationery and Business Cards&nbsp; /&nbsp; Marketing Collateral&nbsp; /&nbsp; Trade Show Graphics and Displays&nbsp; /&nbsp; Print Advertisements&nbsp; /&nbsp; Website with custom CMS</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','portfolio__20110527173630.jpg','on',NULL,'2010-12-21'),(6,1053,'ILR','Independent Living Resources','1',NULL,'<p>. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .</p>\r\n<p>A non-profit organization\\\'s look is updated. The re-brand solidifies their organization as an entity and an accessible website was developed to interact with the visually and hearing impaired.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div>Branding&nbsp; /&nbsp;&nbsp;Stationery and Business Cards&nbsp; /&nbsp; Brochures and Collateral&nbsp; /&nbsp; Website with CMS</div>','portfolio__20110527172418.jpg','on',NULL,'2010-12-21'),(8,1053,'MYRA','Women\'s Health Program','1',NULL,'<p>. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .</p>\r\n<p>A private practice in Walnut Creek, the Women\\\'s Health Program needed a professional look with a feminine touch. Style, color and copy are specifically developed to suit the taste of women.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\\\"\\\">Logo&nbsp; /&nbsp; Marketing Collateral&nbsp; /&nbsp; Stationery&nbsp; /&nbsp; Copywriting&nbsp; /&nbsp; Web Page</p>','portfolio__20110527175528.jpg','on',NULL,'2010-12-21'),(9,1053,'SHL','Sherese Lopez Realty','1',NULL,'<p>. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .</p>\r\n<p>A prominent Contra Costa County realtor is branded. Her logo is striking and visually distinguishes herself from more common realtor branding.</p>\r\n<p>Branding&nbsp; /&nbsp; Stationery &amp; Business Cards&nbsp; /&nbsp; Social Media Setup&nbsp; /&nbsp; Direct Mail Campaign</p>','portfolio__20110527174709.jpg','on',NULL,'2010-12-21'),(10,1053,'CDP','California Document Preparers, Logo Design','2',NULL,'<p>. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .  . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .  . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .</p>\r\n<p>California Document  Preparers underwent a complete re-brand after they broke away from their  franchise. The new logo needed to retain the same look and feel, but  be different enough to distinguish themselves as a separate entity. The re-brand was matched with a comprehensive marketing  strategy which included printed advertisements, mailers and an online  presence.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Logo Rebrand&nbsp; /&nbsp; Business Collateral&nbsp; /&nbsp; Brochure &amp; Marketing  Pieces&nbsp; /&nbsp; Print Advertising&nbsp; /&nbsp; Social Media /&nbsp; Trade Show Graphics&nbsp; /&nbsp;  Website with CMS</p>','portfolio__20110527163601.jpg','on',NULL,'2011-01-31'),(11,1076,'1','Executive Mindshare MultiMedia Video','1','w8x2ANu28ZQ','<p><strong>Witness the Evolution of Social Media. </strong>AG&nbsp;Design Group was commissioned by San Francisco-based Executive Mindshare to produce a multimedia video that documented the evolution of social media and introduced Executive Mindshare\\\'s pilot network, www.biomindshare.com.</p>\r\n<p>This visually engaging and immensely graphic video was featured during Executive Mindshare\\\'s launch party late 2010. &quot;We mixed statistical information with cutting edge graphics to draw the viewer in.&quot; says Santos, AG Design Group\\\'s CEO. &quot;Our goal was to capture the viewer\\\'s attention through visual storytelling. It was a success.&quot;</p>\r\n<p>Executive Mindshare is a vertical business network that combines a business oriented social network with a user-ranked news network for the Life Sciences industry.</p>','featured__20110526154126.jpg','on',NULL,'2011-02-15'),(24,1076,'1','Executive Mindshare','2',NULL,'<p>In the Know</p>','featured__20110527113253.jpg','on',NULL,'2011-05-26'),(25,1076,'1','Executive Mindshare ','3',NULL,'<p>Skyline</p>','featured__20110527113409.jpg','on',NULL,'2011-05-26'),(14,1053,'KAL','Karlson & Lane Logo','1',NULL,'<p>Karlsson &amp; Lane, an accountancy incorporation, wanted a look that was strong, classic and vibrant.</p>\r\n<p>+Logo<br />\r\n+Collateral</p>','portfolio__20110503165038.jpg',NULL,NULL,'2011-05-03'),(15,1053,'EAN','E\'Angelo Trattoria','1',NULL,'<p>. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .  . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .  . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .</p>\r\n<p>E\\\'Angelo Trattoria is located in San Francisco,&nbsp;CA&nbsp;on Chestnut Street. This small restaurant features classic Italian dishes. AG Design created a website that featured the dishes in a simple elegance.</p>\r\n<p>Logo&nbsp; /&nbsp; Website&nbsp; /&nbsp; Menus</p>','portfolio__20110527164416.jpg','on',NULL,'2011-05-03'),(16,1053,'LSA','ASAP Brochure','2',NULL,'<div>. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .  . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .  . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>This  new product, a subsidiary brand of Larson and Shores Architects,  underwent an extensive identity study and branding. AGD further  developed their brand through print advertisements, marketing collateral  and a website. A unique and colorful brochure accentuate the product and the brand.</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>Branding&nbsp; /&nbsp; Stationery and Business Cards&nbsp; /